.SH NAME
rio_dev_get \- Increments the reference count of the RIO device structure
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct rio_dev *" rio_dev_get
.BI "(struct rio_dev *rdev "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "rdev" 12
RIO device being referenced
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Each live reference to a device should be refcounted.

Drivers for RIO devices should normally record such references in
their \fBprobe\fP methods, when they bind to a device, and release
them by calling \fBrio_dev_put\fP, in their \fBdisconnect\fP methods.
